StatementsGoods and Services
Promoting public awareness of issues of interest to football fans and of issues of interest to and in support of charitable fundraising, military veterans, community service, community involvement, bullying prevention and youth behavior; charitable services, namely, promoting public awareness of issues of interest to football fan and of issues of interest to and in support of charitable fundraising, military veterans, community service, community involvement, bullying prevention and youth behavior; production of public service announcements; charitable services, namely, organizing and conducting volunteer programs and community service projects; promoting public awareness as to the need for community involvement in charities and charitable fundraising by hosting and sponsoring charity events

Goods and Services
Charitable fundraising services; philanthropic services concerning monetary donations; charitable fundraising services and philanthropic services concerning monetary donations in support of educational and community needs; charitable fundraising services and philanthropic services concerning monetary donations in connection with professional football games and exhibitions

Goods and Services
Education and entertainment services in the nature of professional football games and exhibitions; providing sports and entertainment information via a global computer network or a commercial on-line computer service or by cable, satellite, television and radio; production of radio and television programs; presentation of live shows featuring football games, football exhibitions, football competitions, and musical and dance performances; organizing sporting events and sporting exhibitions in the nature of football, and organizing events for cultural purposes; organizing community sporting events; distribution of television programming to cable and satellite television systems; entertainment services in the nature of presenting live and prerecorded cheerleader performances at professional football games and exhibitions and personal appearances by cheerleaders; entertainment services, namely, personal appearances by a professional football mascot; providing information services in the field of sports; entertainment services, namely, providing a web site featuring non-downloadable commentary, videos, clips, photographs and other multimedia materials related to sports; entertainment, namely, live music concerts; fan clubs; entertainment media production services for radio, television, video-on-demand, podcast, Internet and stadium facilities; entertainment services, namely, providing live and on-line non-downloadable prerecorded entertainment in the nature of professional football games, football exhibitions, football competitions, athletic competitions, athletic events and musical and dance performances and live and prerecorded sports programming, namely, television programs in the field of sports, and musical and dance performances, ongoing multimedia program featuring sports, and musical and dance performances for arena video systems and broadcast, cable, satellite, Internet, and wireless television, Internet and wireless radio; providing radio, television, video-on-demand, podcast and Internet broadcast audio or video studio facilities; entertainment services in the nature of presenting live and prerecorded cheerleading performances and shows; entertainment services in the nature of presenting live and prerecorded drum performances and shows; entertainment services in the nature of ongoing television programs in the field of children's entertainment; education and entertainment services, namely, ongoing television public service announcements and ongoing television programs in the fields of sports, charitable fundraising, military veterans, community service, community involvement, bullying prevention and youth behavior; providing education and entertainment services in the nature of live and non-downloadable pre-recorded multimedia educational and entertainment content in the fields of sports, charitable fundraising, military veterans, community service, community involvement, bullying prevention and youth behavior via a global computer network or a commercial on-line computer service or by cable, satellite, television and radio
